data.description: Back on the market not the fault of the property.  This fabulous single story home sits on 2.05 (net) acres in the Heart of Temecula Wine Country and this property is almost completely landscaped with a variety of fruit trees, flowering shrubs and Concord grapes. Just minutes from Wineries, Pala Casino, Pechanga Casino and Old Town Temecula. Private driveway leading to circular driveway. Three car detached garage (may be converted to an ADU). Built 2005. Entertainer’s kitchen and walk-in pantry. 3 Bedroom, Den/Optional 4th Bedroom, Living room, Family room and 2 Baths. Large covered patio to view and enjoy the pool and spa. Views to the north. Tons of parking for your guests, toys and ample room for horses or to build that guest house, dream shop or barn. View Hot Air Balloons in the morning. Step away from the busy world at this very private retreat with citrus groves to the south and west of the subject. During spring the blossom fragrance is intoxicating.
